Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the previous episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,they found Mecha-Goat’s goggles by the seaside,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,leading them to worry about his safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, Wolffy found clues that located Mecha-Goat,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but this time, Mecha-Goat’s personality has greatly changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Mecha-Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Mecha-Goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Target spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ancient martial arts program, activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Werewolf,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,what in the world have you done with Mecha-Goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See how powerful I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the consequences of messing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s so strong now that he even hits me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat is out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:02:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Targets spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys can keep fighting. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, don’t hurt Mecha-Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be telling him to not hurt us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic Airplanes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s attacking everyone, no matter who.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry and put the new chip in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But the chip needs some time to restore the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We can’t even get near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Targets spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Targets
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,all cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have I run into this guy again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t let him see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Target spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to chase me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Allen! Flat-Beak Allen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, Allen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Flat-Beak Allen! Allen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Allen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll protect you with my life, Allen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll protect you with my next life, Allen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t think you’d use whatever means necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to get my autograph faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can’t win with you, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Mecha-Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed with the plan, Jonie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But… But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re doing all of this for Mecha-Goat’s own good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat, I’m Jonie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still remember—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still remember this pair of goggles?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your plan worked, Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m really something, aren’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I had Slowy add a hypnosis program to the goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Mecha-Goat wears it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we’ll be able to briefly control him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This hypnosis program only lasts one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry and put in the chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it have fallen out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere near the canyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let’s hurry to the canyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the Magic Airplanes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, hurry and locate the chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to recover Mecha-Goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The canyon is right up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy and I will distract Mecha-Goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of you, get the chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You won’t get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonie! Paddi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s someone in the bushes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie! Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just destroy the chip,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and that’ll be how the story ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun vanishing along with the chip, Mecha-Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, you were the one who helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it’s my turn to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get Jonie medical attention right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To help…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To help…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,are not enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,are my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them to Rainbow for medical attention right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, go pick up the restoration chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonie’s awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi? Weslie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, you’re okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’s ​​Mecha-Goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you risking your life to protect him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he’s now fully recovered with our chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Jonie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re welcome.
